{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dc9d480e3f","title":"关于红军作战的原则","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ce0276d455","index":0,"year":1937,"month":8,"day":1,"articleId":"dc9d480e3f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji10","name":"毛泽东全集第10卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji10.pdf"},{"id":"wenji2","name":"毛泽东文集第二卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji10":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"adde8c9e2d","type":"paragraph","text":"关于红军作战的原则","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"dc9d480e3f"},{"id":"a1f4c148ee","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年8月1日）周、博、林关于红军作战，依当前敌我情况，我们认为须坚持下列两原则：甲、在整个战路方针下执行独立自主的分散作战的游击战争，而不是阵地战，也不是集中作战，因此不能在战役战术上受束续。只有如此才能发挥红军特长，给日寇以相当打击乙、依上述原则，在开始阶段，红军以出三分之一的兵力为适宜，兵力过大，不能发挥游击战，而易受故人的集中打击。其余兵力依战争发展，逐渐使用之以上原则，请与客同志商定，并准各携告国民党","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"dc9d480e3f"},{"id":"61a87f272f","type":"paragraph","text":"洛毛","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"dc9d480e3f"},{"id":"1144a05e00","type":"paragraph","text":"东西[1]周，指周思来。海，指博古，秦邦宪（1907-1946）.江苏无的同国民党进行该判的代表。[2]指当时在陕西省泾阳县云阳镇的朱德、彭德怀等红军总部领导人。[3]洛，指洛甫，即张闻天（1900-1976），江苏南汇（今属上海市）","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"dc9d480e3f"}],"page":{"id":"77d4c40832","publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"dc9d480e3f","start":507,"end":507}},"wenji2":{"comments":[{"id":"242c6dcc2a","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据中央档案馆保存的抄件刊印。"},{"id":"2aa865781e","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f","index":2,"part_index":5,"offset":10,"text":"指当时在陕西泾阳县云阳镇的朱德、彭德怀等红军总部领导人。"},{"id":"6e196bfe34","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f","index":3,"part_index":6,"offset":1,"text":"洛，指洛甫，即张闻天（一九○○——一九七六），江苏南汇（今属上海市）人。当时任中共中央政治局常委，在中央负总责。"},{"id":"873eac1a15","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f","index":1,"part_index":1,"offset":5,"text":"周，指周恩来。博，指博古，即秦邦宪（一九○七——一九四六），江苏无锡人。林，指林伯渠（一八八六——一九六○），湖南临澧人。他们当时是中共中央委派的同国民党进行谈判的代表。"}],"contents":[{"id":"040c44468b","type":"paragraph","text":"洛、毛","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f"},{"id":"17ffcbbb87","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、依上述原则，在开始阶段，红军以出三分之一的兵力为适宜，兵力过大，不能发挥游击战，而易受敌人的集中打击。其余兵力依战争发展，逐渐使用之。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f"},{"id":"18091eaad3","type":"paragraph","text":"以上原则，请与各同志商定，并准备携告国民党。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f"},{"id":"2aa865781e","type":"paragraph","text":"关于红军作战，依当前敌我情况，我们认为须坚持下列两原则：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f"},{"id":"4307972c54","type":"paragraph","text":"东酉","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f"},{"id":"6e196bfe34","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、在整个战略方针下执行独立自主的分散作战的游击战争，而不是阵地战，也不是集中作战，因此不能在战役战术上受束缚。只有如此才能发挥红军特长，给日寇以相当打击。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f"},{"id":"873eac1a15","type":"appellation","text":"周、博、林：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f"},{"id":"d11a69e47d","type":"title","text":"关于红军作战的原则","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f"}],"page":{"id":"0585127850","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"dc9d480e3f","start":14,"end":14}}}},"__N_SSG":true}